data.title: 150 Canadian Films
data.meta_description: 150 Canadian Films - Free download as PDF File (.pdf), Text File (.txt) or view presentation slides online. The document discusses two events celebrating Canadian films as part of Canada's 150th anniversary celebrations: National Canadian Film Day and 150 Canadian Films. The Prime Minister and Minister of Canadian Heritage express their support for the events and their goal of celebrating and discovering Canada's film industry. The document then provides an introduction and legend for the list of 150 Canadian films selected for the events, highlighting the diversity of Canadian cinema.
